### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Get Session (requires valid Supabase token)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/session
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_SUPABASE_TOKEN_HERE

### List Profiles (requires authentication)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/profiles
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_SUPABASE_TOKEN_HERE

### Create Profile (requires authentication)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/profiles
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_SUPABASE_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "relationship": "self",
  "dob": "1990-01-15T00:00:00.000Z",
  "gender": "male"
}

### Get Specific Profile (requires authentication)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/profiles/PROFILE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_SUPABASE_TOKEN_HERE

### Update Profile (requires authentication)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/profiles/PROFILE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_SUPABASE_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Smith",
  "dob": "1990-01-15T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### Set as Default Profile (requires authentication)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/profiles/PROFILE_ID_HERE/default
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_SUPABASE_TOKEN_HERE

### Delete Profile (requires authentication)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/profiles/PROFILE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_SUPABASE_TOKEN_HERE
